quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:653,&quot;width&quot;:979,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:710,&quot;bytes&quot;:62914,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F200bdd18-a6c4-4583-852d-1a7fc2301ec8_979x653.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F200bdd18-a6c4-4583-852d-1a7fc2301ec8_979x653.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F200bdd18-a6c4-4583-852d-1a7fc2301ec8_979x653.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F200bdd18-a6c4-4583-852d-1a7fc2301ec8_979x653.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption"> <a href="https://unsplash.com/@diegitane?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">迭戈·费尔南德斯</a>(Diego Fernandez) 在<a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/black-and-red-ship-on-body-of-water-at-daytime-6Vg8N8u61aI?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Unsplash</a>上拍摄的照片</figcaption></figure></div><p>本周的重大经济新闻是拜登对多种中国制造的商品<a href="https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2024/05/14/fact-sheet-president-biden-takes-action-to-protect-american-workers-and-businesses-from-chinas-unfair-trade-practices/">征收巨额关税</a>。这些关税似乎成为印度、巴西、越南、泰国、墨西哥、欧盟等其他国家<a href="https://x.com/BrianCDeese/status/1790815108915933515">考虑对中国征收关税</a>的催化剂。换句话说，现在，世界上大部分地区都将<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-decade-of-the-second-china-shock">第二次中国冲击</a>视为对自己的制造业的危险，并且正在采取相应的行动。</p><p>这是一个巨大的重大转变。一年半前，当<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-end-of-the-system-of-the-world">我宣布</a>定义过去2-3年的全球经济体系现在正在崩溃时，有些人自然认为我夸大了我的案子。现在，即使是对这一转变的批评者也被迫承认 <a href="https://www.economist.com/briefing/2024/05/09/the-worlds-economic-order-is-breaking-down">一个新时代即将到来</a>。</p><p>在接下来的几年中，脱钩，竞争和分裂的时代对世界意味着世界，以及如何有效地管理世界的时代，将成为大量讨论和分析（以及Noahpinion博客文章）的主题。但是目前，我认为应该有更多想法的一个有趣的问题是：<em>中国为什么要出口这么多东西？</em>我们看到的大多数新的贸易壁垒和工业政策都直接或间接与中国有关。新的关税是针对中国制造商品的巨大贸易盈余的回应： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa94ce5ef-bd23-4f18-84a6-6b03da608f60_680x494.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa94ce5ef-bd23-4f18-84a6-6b03da608f60_680x494.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa94ce5ef-bd23-4f18-84a6-6b03da608f60_680x494.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa94ce5ef-bd23-4f18-84a6-6b03da608f60_680x494.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%