/2000/svg"><path classname="inner-triangle" d="M10 8L16 12L10 16V8Z" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div><span class="embedded-post-cta">现在听</span></div><div class="embedded-post-meta">9 days ago · 8 likes · 6 comments · Brad DeLong and Noah Smith</div></div><p> And I also have another “mailbag” episode of Econ 102, where I answer a bunch of questions from listeners: </p><iframe class="spotify-wrap podcast" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6765630000ba8ae6c76488a10c74561202b3d3&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;How the Fed Works, Currency Crises, and TikTok ban [Listener Mailbag]&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith, Erik Torenberg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Episode&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/episode/1iOSIs4ET1oGC2GUmb4iDn&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/1iOSIs4ET1oGC2GUmb4iDn" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p> Anyway, on to this week&#39;s list of interesting things!</p><h4> 1. The Palestine protests don&#39;t represent the young generation</h4><p> I&#39;m pretty tired of writing about the Palestine protests. I said pretty much all that I wanted to say in <a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/palestine-is-the-end-of-the-line">my post two weeks ago</a> , and my central point was that the whole movement is kind of boring. But I feel like I should post the results of this recent poll, because it pretty much vindicates what I was saying.</p><p> Generation Lab surveyed 1250 college kids, asking them to pick up to three issues they thought were important. Only 13% mentioned Palestine at all: </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8549e2ca-f248-4f47-8b5a-f82934e8739f_917x611.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8549e2ca-f248-4f47-8b5a-f82934e8739f_917x611.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8549e2ca-f248-4f47-8b5a-f82934e8739f_917x611.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8549e2ca-f248-4f47-8b5a-f82934e8739f_917x611.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8549e2ca-f248-4f47-8b5a-f82934e8739f_917x611.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8549e2ca-f248-4f47-8b5a-f82934e8739f_917x611.jpeg" width="648" height="431.76444929116684" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8549e2ca-f248-4f47-8b5a-f82934e8739f_917x611.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:611,&quot;width&quot;:917,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:648,&quot;bytes&quot;:99038,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_a